Jevans’ RFU pay-off

The size of Debbie Jevans' six-figure pay-off from the RFU after walking out as chief executive of England Rugby 2015 points to Twickenham’s high command wanting her out — even if she made the first move.

It is understood the breakdown of Jevans’ relationships with the RFU leadership included those with affable chairman Bill Beaumont as well as chief executive Ian Ritchie.

